\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}1 pound dry red {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/kidney-bean/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 kidney beans}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 quarts water\
